      "text": "\n---\n\n## TECH STACK\n- Frontend: React 18 + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS\n- Backend: Node.js + Express (or Firebase Functions)\n- Storage: Firebase Storage (or Supabase)\n- Database: Firestore (or PostgreSQL)\n- Auth: Firebase Auth (Google + Email)\n- AI/ML: Google Cloud Vision API + Gemini API for market detection\n\n---\n\n## CORE FEATURES\n\n### 1. MARKET AUTO-DETECT ENGINE\n- Integrate Google Cloud Vision API or Gemini 1.5 Pro to analyze uploaded \n  product images or documents\n- Auto-detect product category, price range, target audience, \n  and best-fit marketplace (eBay, Etsy, Amazon, Shopify, etc.)\n- Display a confidence score (0–100%) per detected market\n- Allow user to override auto-detected market before proceeding\n\n### 2. FILE UNLOADER (Upload System)\n- Drag-and-drop upload zone accepting: images (JPG, PNG, WEBP), \n  video (MP4, MOV), PDF, CSV product lists\n- Batch upload support (up to 50 files simultaneously)\n- Real-time upload progress bar per file\n- File preview thumbnails after upload\n- Auto-categorize files by type (image, video, document)\n- Store files in Firebase Storage with organized folder structure: \n  /uploads/{userId}/{sessionId}/{filename}\n\n### 3. PROCESSING CONTROLS PANEL\nBuild a sidebar control panel with:\n- [ ] Market Selector: dropdown of detected + manual markets\n- [ ] Product Title Generator: AI-powered using Gemini API\n- [ ] Description Writer: auto-generate SEO product descriptions\n- [ ] Pricing Suggester: based on market + category data\n- [ ] Hashtag/Tag Generator for social platforms\n- [ ] Image Enhancer toggle (brightness, contrast, background removal)\n- [ ] Watermark toggle with custom text input\n- [ ] Format Converter: resize output for each platform \n      (1:1 for Instagram, 16:9 for YouTube, etc.)\n- Processing queue with start/pause/cancel controls\n- Live processing log (console-style output panel)\n\n### 4. DOWNLOAD BUTTON + EXPORT SYSTEM\n- Single-file download button per processed asset\n- \"Download All\" button → generates ZIP archive client-side using JSZip\n- Export format selector: original, PNG, WEBP, MP4, PDF\n- Export presets per platform: \"Export for Shopify\", \n  \"Export for Etsy\", \"Export for Instagram\"\n- Download history panel showing past exports with timestamps\n\n### 5. MULTIMEDIA SHARING PLATFORM (Final Output Hub)\n- Gallery view of all processed outputs (grid + list toggle)\n- One-click share links: generate a public URL per asset or full session\n- Direct share buttons for: Instagram, Facebook, TikTok, Pinterest, \n  Twitter/X, WhatsApp, Email\n- Embed code generator (iframe snippet) for each asset\n- QR Code generator for each product/session link\n- \"Publish to Marketplace\" button (webhook-ready for Shopify/WooCommerce API)\n- Collaboration: invite team members via email to view/download session\n\n---\n\n## UI/UX REQUIREMENTS\n- Dark mode by default with light mode toggle\n- Responsive: mobile-first, fully functional on tablet and desktop\n- Left sidebar: navigation (Upload, Process, Gallery, Share, Settings)\n- Main content area: dynamic based on active step\n- Top bar: user avatar, session name (editable), notifications bell\n- Step indicator: Upload → Detect → Process → Export → Share (5-step wizard)\n- Toast notifications for all async actions\n- Loading skeletons for all data-fetching states\n- Empty states with clear CTAs when no files are uploaded\n\n---\n\n## DATA MODELS\n\n### Session\n{\n  id: string,\n  userId: string,\n  name: string,\n  createdAt: timestamp,\n  status: \u0027uploading\u0027 | \u0027detecting\u0027 | \u0027processing\u0027 | \u0027complete\u0027,\n  detectedMarkets: Market[],\n  files: FileAsset[],\n  exports: Export[]\n}\n\n### FileAsset\n{\n  id: string,\n  sessionId: string,\n  originalName: string,\n  type: \u0027image\u0027 | \u0027video\u0027 | \u0027document\u0027,\n  storageUrl: string,\n  thumbnailUrl: string,\n  detectedCategory: string,\n  processingStatus: \u0027pending\u0027 | \u0027processing\u0027 | \u0027done\u0027 | \u0027error\u0027,\n  processedOutputs: ProcessedOutput[]\n}\n\n### Market\n{\n  name: string,\n  platform: string,\n  confidenceScore: number,\n  suggestedPrice: number,\n  tags: string[]\n}\n\n---\n\n## API ROUTES (Express)\nPOST   /api/sessions              → create new session\nGET    /api/sessions/:id          → get session details\nPOST   /api/upload                → handle file upload to storage\nPOST   /api/detect                → run market auto-detection on files\nPOST   /api/process               → start processing job with selected controls\nGET    /api/process/:jobId/status → poll processing job status\nPOST   /api/export                → generate export package\nGET    /api/share/:sessionId      → get public share data for a session\n\n---\n\n## SECURITY \u0026 PERFORMANCE\n- All routes protected with Firebase Auth JWT middleware\n- File size limits: images 20MB, video 500MB, documents 50MB\n- Rate limiting: 100 API requests/minute per user\n- Lazy load all gallery images\n- Web Workers for client-side ZIP generation (non-blocking UI)\n- Error boundaries on all major React component trees\n\n---\n\nBuild the complete application with all components, routes, and \nFirebase configuration. Start with the main App layout, then \nimplement each feature module in order: Upload → Detect → Process \n→ Export → Share.\n",
